---
import BaseLayout from "../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
import { getCollection } from "astro:content";
import RecommendedOrder from "../../components/RecommendedOrder.astro";

const allPosts = await getCollection("posts", ({ data }) => !data.draft);

const ayanBreadcrumbData = {
  "@context": "https://schema.org",
  "@type": "BreadcrumbList",
  "itemListElement": [
    { "@type": "ListItem", "position": 1, "name": "首页", "item": "https://amz.hao1234.top/" },
    { "@type": "ListItem", "position": 2, "name": "广告 PPC", "item": "https://amz.hao1234.top/ppc/" }
  ]
};
---
<BaseLayout title="亚马逊广告 PPC｜ACOS、关键词与广告复盘" description="整理亚马逊广告 PPC 运营方法，覆盖 ACOS、TACOS、CTR、CVR、搜索词报告、否词和预算优化。">
  <script type="application/ld+json" set:html={JSON.stringify(ayanBreadcrumbData)}></script>
  <section class="page-hero">
    <div class="page-hero-inner">
      <h1>亚马逊广告 PPC</h1>
      <p>围绕新品广告、关键词、否词、ACOS、TACOS 和广告报表复盘建立实战 SOP。</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section">
    <div class="topic-intro">
      <h2>广告不是花钱的工具，是判断市场的仪表盘</h2>
      <p>很多卖家把广告当成成本项，越看 ACOS 越焦虑。其实广告的真正价值，是让你用真金白银把市场"扫一遍"，知道哪些词值得、哪些词不值得。</p>
      <p>本专题的思路是：先有第一周数据，再谈第二周优化。新品期不要追 ACOS，稳态期才追 ACOS。这个节奏一旦搞反，后面所有动作都会变形。</p>
    </div>

    <a class="guide-card" href="/articles/ppc-learning-path/">
      <div class="guide-card-hint">推荐先读 · 学习路径</div>
      <h3>亚马逊 PPC 广告学习路径：从结构搭建到数据判断</h3>
      <p>把 PPC 优化拆成 4 步：结构搭建、报表复盘、否词和预算、诊断迭代。按顺序跟读，能在自己的广告活动上跑通完整闭环。</p>
      <span class="guide-card-cta">看完整学习路径 →</span>
    </a>

    <RecommendedOrder topic="ppc" allPosts={allPosts} title="推荐学习顺序" />

    <a class="resource-strip" href="/resources/" aria-label="查看 PPC 配套资料包">
      <div class="resource-strip-text">
        <div class="resource-strip-hint">本专题配套资料包</div>
        <h3>把广告复盘沉淀为周复盘、否词与预算模板</h3>
        <p>3 张表 + 1 套周节奏,覆盖周复盘、否词清单、预算分配表和新品期首周检查表。</p>
        <ul class="resource-strip-chips">
          <li>周复盘表</li>
          <li>否词清单</li>
          <li>预算分配</li>
          <li>首周检查</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
      <span class="resource-strip-cta">查看资料包 →</span>
    </a>

    <div class="grid grid-3">
      <a class="card" href="/articles/ai-ppc-report-review/"><h3>如何用 AI 复盘亚马逊广告报表</h3><p>从指标变化判断问题类型。</p></a>
      <a class="card" href="/articles/new-product-ppc-week-one/"><h3>新品广告第一周怎么开</h3><p>预算、关键词和否词的基础框架。</p></a>
      <a class="card" href="/articles/sp-ad-structure/"><h3>SP 广告结构：自动、精准、词组、竞品怎么分工</h3><p>把 4 类活动的角色讲清楚，避免乱搭。</p></a>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  .topic-intro {
    max-width: 880px;
    margin: 0 0 28px;
    padding: 24px 28px;
    background: linear-gradient(180deg, #ffffff 0%, #fbfdff 100%);
    border: 1px solid rgba(226, 232, 240, 0.95);
    border-radius: 20px;
    box-shadow:
      0 14px 40px rgba(15, 23, 42, 0.05),
      inset 0 1px 0 rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.95);
  }

  .topic-intro h2 {
    margin: 0 0 14px;
    font-size: 22px;
    color: #0f172a;
    letter-spacing: -0.3px;
    position: relative;
    padding-left: 12px;
  }

  .topic-intro h2::before {
    content: "";
    position: absolute;
    left: 0;
    top: 4px;
    width: 4px;
    height: 22px;
    border-radius: 999px;
    background: #1368ff;
  }

  .topic-intro p {
    margin: 0 0 12px;
    color: #475569;
    line-height: 1.85;
    font-size: 15px;
  }

  .topic-intro p:last-child {
    margin-bottom: 0;
  }

  .guide-card {
    display: block;
    margin: 0 0 24px;
    padding: 24px 28px;
    border-radius: 20px;
    background:
      linear-gradient(135deg, #eef5ff 0%, #f0f7ff 100%);
    border: 1px solid #cfe0ff;
    box-shadow:
      0 14px 40px rgba(19, 104, 255, 0.10),
      inset 0 1px 0 rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.9);
    text-decoration: none;
    color: inherit;
    transition: transform 0.15s ease, box-shadow 0.15s ease, border-color 0.15s ease;
    position: relative;
    overflow: hidden;
  }

  .guide-card::before {
    content: "";
    position: absolute;
    left: 0;
    top: 0;
    width: 4px;
    height: 100%;
    background: linear-gradient(180deg, #1368ff, #7dd3fc);
  }

  .guide-card:hover {
    transform: translateY(-2px);
    border-color: #93c5fd;
    box-shadow:
      0 22px 56px rgba(19, 104, 255, 0.18),
      inset 0 1px 0 rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.95);
  }

  .guide-card-hint {
    font-size: 11px;
    color: #1368ff;
    font-weight: 900;
    letter-spacing: 0.4px;
    margin-bottom: 10px;
  }

  .guide-card h3 {
    margin: 0 0 10px;
    color: #0f172a;
    font-size: 20px;
    line-height: 1.4;
  }

  .guide-card p {
    margin: 0 0 14px;
    color: #475569;
    line-height: 1.85;
    font-size: 15px;
  }

  .guide-card-cta {
    color: #1368ff;
    font-weight: 900;
    font-size: 14px;
  }

  .resource-strip {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: space-between;
    gap: 20px;
    margin: 0 0 28px;
    padding: 20px 24px;
    border-radius: 16px;
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, #fffcf0 0%, #fef6e0 100%);
    border: 1px solid #f4d089;
    box-shadow:
      0 10px 28px rgba(217, 119, 6, 0.08),
      inset 0 1px 0 rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.9);
    text-decoration: none;
    color: inherit;
    transition: transform 0.15s ease, box-shadow 0.15s ease, border-color 0.15s ease;
    position: relative;
    overflow: hidden;
  }

  .resource-strip::before {
    content: "";
    position: absolute;
    left: 0;
    top: 0;
    width: 4px;
    height: 100%;
    background: linear-gradient(180deg, #d97706, #f59e0b);
  }

  .resource-strip:hover {
    transform: translateY(-2px);
    border-color: #d97706;
    box-shadow:
      0 16px 40px rgba(217, 119, 6, 0.18),
      inset 0 1px 0 rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.95);
  }

  .resource-strip-text {
    flex: 1 1 auto;
    min-width: 0;
  }

  .resource-strip-hint {
    font-size: 11px;
    color: #b45309;
    font-weight: 900;
    letter-spacing: 0.4px;
    margin-bottom: 8px;
  }

  .resource-strip h3 {
    margin: 0 0 8px;
    color: #0f172a;
    font-size: 17px;
    line-height: 1.4;
    letter-spacing: -0.2px;
  }

  .resource-strip p {
    margin: 0 0 12px;
    color: #57534e;
    line-height: 1.7;
    font-size: 14px;
  }

  .resource-strip-chips {
    list-style: none;
    margin: 0;
    padding: 0;
    display: flex;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    gap: 6px;
  }

  .resource-strip-chips li {
    display: inline-block;
    padding: 4px 10px;
    background: #ffffff;
    border: 1px solid #f4d089;
    border-radius: 999px;
    font-size: 12px;
    color: #92400e;
    font-weight: 700;
  }

  .resource-strip-cta {
    flex: 0 0 auto;
    color: #b45309;
    font-weight: 900;
    font-size: 14px;
    white-space: nowrap;
  }

  @media (max-width: 720px) {
    .resource-strip {
      flex-direction: column;
      align-items: flex-start;
    }
    .resource-strip-cta {
      align-self: flex-start;
    }
  }
</style>
